expressed as the mean &#x000b1; standard deviation or the number (%).</p></fn></table-wrap-foot></table-wrap><p>Eleven patients (45.8%) in the placebo group and 18 patients (64.3%) in the 2%
chlorhexidine/toothbrushing group developed VAP (RR=1.4; 95% CI=0.83-2.34; p=0.29).</p><p>The average length of mechanical ventilation was 6 days in the placebo group and 8.5
