(p=0.36). The mortality rate was 46.5% in the 2% chlorhexidine/toothbrushing group and
37.5% in the placebo group (RR=1.24; 95%CI=0.64-2.37; p=0.07).</p><table-wrap id="t02" orientation="portrait" position="float"><label>Table 2</label><caption><p>Outcomes of the placebo and 2% chlorhexidine/toothbrushing groups</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1"><bold>Variables</bold></td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>Placebo N(%)</bold></td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>Chlorhexidine N(%)</bold></td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><bold>p value</bold></td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1">VAP rate</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">11(45.8)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">18(64.3)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.29</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Microbiologically confirmed VAP rate</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">8(72.7)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">12(66.6)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.86</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Duration of intubation (days)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">6 [4-12.7]</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">8.5 [7.3-14.7]</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.17</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" rowspan="1">Duration of intubation</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x000a0;</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x000a0;&#x000a0;&#x000a0;&#x000a0;</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Between 3 and 5 days</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">12(50)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">5(17.8)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.03</td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x000a0;</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Between 6 and 10 days</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">5(20.8)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspa